pullsbody:
Encountered a schema collision with nsm/bro events. In reviewing the guard duty data/schema, there is only one service (guard duty itself) and they refer to the service section as 'findings', which makes more sense: 
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/guardduty/latest/ug/guardduty_findings.html
pull_repo_desc: A simple CloudFormation template to transform GuardDuty events into Mozlla MozDef standard format.
pull_commit_message:
Rename details.service to details.finding

Encountered a schema collision with nsm/bro events. In reviewing the guard duty data/schema, there is only one service (guard duty itself) and they refer to the service section as 'findings', which makes more sense: 
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/guardduty/latest/ug/guardduty_findings.html
